latestPosts.caption:
Aukat se bahar race sign kar li hai… aur ab darr lag raha hai 💀
Par 60 din hain, aur har din ka hisaab yahan milega.
Hyrox India — international level ki ek aisi fitness race jisme 8 workouts + 8 km run ka combo hai.
Main is waqt us level pe nahi hoon… lekin roz ka ek kadam, aukat badal sakta hai.
Agar aap bhi kisi cheez se fight kar rahe ho — discipline, motivation, body image — let’s grow together.
Ye journey real hai, raw hai… aur public hai.
Welcome to Episode 1: #AukatSeBahar 🥵🔥
#HyroxPrep #FitnessReel #GirlsWhoLift #IndiaFitness #RacePrep #BurpeeBroadJump #HyroxIndia2025”
🩵🏝️🌊
